 <title>Water Power: The Future Vision Under New Director Alejandro Moreno</title>
 <link>https://energy.gov/eere/articles/water-power-future-vision-under-new-director-alejandro-moreno</link>
 <description>&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div  property=&quot;content:encoded&quot; class=&quot;field-item odd&quot;&gt; &lt;p&gt;Alejandro Moreno recently joined the Water Power Technologies Office as director and will lead the hydropower and marine and hydrokinetic portfolios. Moreno returns to the Energy Department after positions at the International Finance Corporation and The World Bank. He lays out his thoughts on hydropower and his goals for the office.&lt;/p&gt;
