 <title>Pumped-Storage Hydropower Shows Promise for Boosting Energy Storage</title>
 <link>https://energy.gov/eere/articles/pumped-storage-hydropower-shows-promise-boosting-energy-storage</link>
 <description>&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div  property=&quot;content:encoded&quot; class=&quot;field-item odd&quot;&gt; &lt;p&gt;As a major clean energy contributor, U.S. hydropower plays an important role today for both electricity generation and energy storage. For more than 100 years, U.S. hydropower has been an important source of low-cost, low-emissions renewable energy.&lt;/p&gt;
